cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

The paper proposes a framework for reducing energy consumption in DNN training, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several CS sub-fields such as machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and control systems (cs.SY). Given that the paper focuses on DNN training, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG and cs.CV, which are the two most relevant sub-categories. However, since the paper also discusses optimization and energy estimation, it could also be classified under cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.SY.
